wikipedia_page.main: Nathaniel Ashley Thomas Watkins (born 7 November 1991) is a Jersey international cricketer. He also played three seasons with Durham MCCU, including a number of first-class games, and also appeared in several minor counties matches for Oxfordshire. Watkins is a right-handed batsman who bowls slow left-arm orthodox spin.
